    <briefdescription>
<para>This file contains a self test example using the Interrupt Controller driver (<ref refid="struct_x_intc" kindref="compound">XIntc</ref>) and hardware device. </para>    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Please reference other device driver examples to see more examples of how the Intc and interrupts can be used by a software application.</para><para>This example shows the use of the Interrupt Controller both with a PowerPC405 and MicroBlaze processor.</para><para>The TestApp Gen utility uses this file to perform the self test and setup of Intc for interrupts.</para><para><simplesect kind="note"><para></para></simplesect>
